          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where Craft Meets Beauty"
          }
        },
        "text_pxNH7J": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At the heart of the collection is Molly’s enduring love of traditional printmaking. Originally hand carved wood blocks, she has translated these signature motifs into designs that feel both celebratory and considered - where painterly florals, rhythmic pattern and joyful colour come together in harmony.<br/><br/>Learn more about Molly’s printmaking journey and the stories behind her designs.</p>",
            "code": ""
          }
        },
